OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,FITV Border's Kieran MacFadzean went to
OL,7,Fmeet some of the people taking part in
OL,8,Fthe challenge
OL,10,FThe family and friends of Carlisle
OL,11,FUnited and Workington Reds hero Tony
OL,12,FHopper are embarking on their latest
OL,13,Ffundraising challenge.
OL,15,FAround 50 people will be taking part
OL,16,Fin the 100-mile cycle from Carlisle to
OL,17,FEdinburgh on Saturday.
