OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,FThe oldest rider is 70 years old and
OL,7,Fthe youngest is 10-year-old Harry
OL,8,FLittle, who said: "I'm pretty
OL,9,Fconfident about it and I'm looking
OL,10,Fforward to it a lot.
OL,12,F"I enjoy it because I like pushing
OL,13,Fmyself harder than I've ever pushed
OL,14,Fmyself before and I enjoy it because
OL,15,Fwhenever I ride, I normally always
OL,16,Ffind myself laughing at the end."
OL,18,FTony died after being diagnosed with
OL,19,FMotor Neurone Disease in 2018.
