OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,FThe money raised by the riders will go
OL,7,Fto the MND association and Carlisle's
OL,8,FEden Valley Hospice and his family say
OL,9,Fthey hope this challenge will help
OL,10,Fkeep his memory alive.
OL,12,F"That's where he died in 2018 and he
OL,13,Fhad excellent care," said his wife Sue.
OL,15,FShe added: "Both charities really
OL,16,Fhelped us when Tony was suffering.
OL,18,F"They use the funds to actually care
OL,19,Ffor local people, people in Cumbria,
OL,20,Fwho don't just have MND but have a
OL,21,Fpalliative diagnosis.
