OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,F"I just love both charities, so it's
OL,7,Fimportant that we keep that going.
OL,9,F"We're so lucky to have a local
OL,10,Fhospice as well."JSue and Tony's son,
OL,11,FDan Hopper will also be taking part in
OL,12,Fthe challenge on Saturday.
OL,14,FHe said: "It's really important that
OL,15,Fwe do a lot of work to remember my dad
OL,16,Fand raise awareness for him and it's
OL,17,Fsuch a horrible disease and I just
OL,18,Fwant to support anyone that could get
OL,19,FMND."
